headline.main: Press Facilities Badly Confused at Parley; Little News and Poor Transport Provided

lead_paragraph: CAIRO, Egypt, Dec. 1 -- It has been suggested that all dispatches reporting the historic Allied conferences be datelined: "Department of Utter Confusion, Somewhere Overseas."
abstract: Cairo conf press facilities reptd badly confused
